These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: punk, gospel, trance, rock, house, disco
6 different pets are kept: rat, chinchilla, pony, turtle, bird, horse
 1. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5
 3. the fan of house is not the owner of the bird##6
 4. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5
 5. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 7. the owner of the bird is not the fan of gospel##6
 8. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of punk is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the fan of rock##7
10. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
11. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
12. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
13. the owner of the rat is the fan of punk##1
14. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
15. the fan of disco is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | punk | trance   | disco     | gospel    | house   |
| Pet           | bird | rat   | horse | turtle | pony | chinchilla |

