.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: zombie, martial-arts, sports, musical, animation, satire
6 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, pony, cat, rabbit, bird
 1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 7. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching animation movies is not the owner of the rabbit##6
10. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the cat##7
11. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
12. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
14. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
15. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
16. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
17. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the person watching animation movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | satire | musical | animation     | sports      | zombie |
| Pet           | rat         | pony        | rabbit   | cat | ferret | bird    |

