.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, mirinda, coffee, milk, juice
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: sailing, skiing, golf, handball, volleyball, rugby
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is not the person drinking coffee##6
 5. the person drinking fanta is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
 6. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking sprite##7
11. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
13. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
14. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | milk        | coffee | juice    | fanta    | mirinda | sprite |
| Sport      | skiing | volleyball  | rugby | handball | sailing | golf      |

