 8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person drinking coffee##7
10. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
12. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
13. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking coffee##1
14. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
