11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
12. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the owner of the chinchilla and the person driving the car##7
13. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Pet         | horse   | ferret | fish      | guinea-pig | cat  | chinchilla   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | ship  | car | van   | scooter | bus |

