.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: skydiving, woodworking, cooking, reading, magic-tricks, sudoku
The people have 6 different jobs:  lawyer, bartender, nurse, videographer, freelancer, photographer
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the videographer and the bartender##7
 5. the photographer is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the freelancer##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
 8. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 9. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
10. the bartender is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
11. the photographer is on the right of the nurse##1
12. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
14. the bartender is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
15. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | cooking         | reading | woodworking | skydiving   | sudoku | magic-tricks  |
| Job     | freelancer | videographer  | nurse  | photographer | bartender  | lawyer |

 